# Rule Usage

Document which cursor rules were applied during work.

## When to Apply

When completing tasks that followed specific rules or making code changes requiring rule guidance.

## Implementation

After completing a task: review relevant rules, list actively applied rules, add "Rules Applied" section.

## Format

```markdown
## Rules Applied

- [Rule Name](.cursor/rules/category/rule_name.mdc) - How it was used
- [Another Rule](.cursor/rules/category/another_rule.mdc) - Brief description
```

## Example

```markdown
## Rules Applied

- [TypeScript Guidelines](.cursor/rules/guidelines/typescript.mdc) - Type safety and code structure
- [Naming Conventions](.cursor/rules/guidelines/naming.mdc) - snake_case file naming
```

